OL,4,Cwomen in bathroom jailed
OL,6,FA firearms dealer has been jailed
OL,7,Fafter he was found with extreme
OL,8,Fpornography and covert videos of women
OL,9,Ffilmed in a bathroom.
OL,11,FPolice seized Daniel Valmont's laptop
OL,12,Ffrom his home in Rotherham in 2022
OL,13,Fafter reports were made that he had
OL,14,Fbeen sending sexual communications.
OL,16,FA South Yorkshire Police spokesperson
OL,17,Fsaid: "During searches of Valmont's
OL,18,Fdevices, extreme pornography,
OL,19,Fincluding beastiality and voyeuristic
OL,20,Fvideos, where he had filmed women
OL,21,Fsecretly while in the bathroom."
