OL,3,CFirearms dealer who covertly filmed
OL,4,Cwomen in bathroom jailed
OL,6,FValmont, who ran Sheffield-based
OL,7,FValmont Firearms, claimed the videos
OL,8,Fhad been filmed accidentally after he
OL,9,Fforgot to take the cameras out of
OL,10,Fbathrooms when he recorded himself.
OL,12,FHe had his weapons seized. The licence
OL,13,Ffor the business - described online as
OL,14,Fa "family run business...aiming to
OL,15,Fgive a fun, friendly and excellent
OL,16,Fservice to the shooting public" - was
OL,17,Frevoked.
OL,19,FValmont was charged with voyeurism and
OL,20,Fpossessing indecent images of
OL,21,Fbestiality.
