OL,3,CFirearms dealer who covertly filmed
OL,4,Cwomen in bathroom jailed
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty and was jailed for
OL,7,F42 weeks and given a ten-year Sexual
OL,8,FHarm Prevention Order.
OL,10,FInvestigating officer Julie Cooper
OL,11,Fsaid: "Firearms can have devastating
OL,12,Fconsequences and should only be in the
OL,13,Fhands of responsible, upstanding, and
OL,14,Fmorally sound citizens.
OL,16,F"We have strict processes in place to
OL,17,Fensure that those in possession,
OL,18,Fhandling and selling firearms are of a
OL,19,Fsound judgement and a fit and proper
OL,20,Fperson, and Valmont's actions show he
OL,21,Fdoes not reflect this.
